# Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.test`) inside `coco-rs/tests/live/`.
# Both filenames are read; `.env.test` wins when both exist.

# в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Required for DeepSeek tests в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# Same key powers both `deepseek-openai` and `deepseek-anthropic`
# builtin providers. When unset, every DeepSeek test skips gracefully.
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...

# в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Optional gates в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# Allow-list of providers to run (comma list, lowercase). Unset = run all.
# COCO_LIVE_TEST_PROVIDERS=deepseek-openai,deepseek-anthropic

# Capability filter: comma list from {text, streaming, tools, cross_protocol}.
# Unset = all enabled. Use `none` to disable everything (skip all tests).
# COCO_LIVE_TEST_CAPABILITIES=text,streaming

# Custom path to this env file (overrides .env.test / .env discovery).
# COCO_LIVE_TEST_ENV_FILE=/abs/path/to/credentials.env
